                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Grounded Sci-Fi—8 Mind-Bending Movies That Never Leave Earth]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/grounded-sci-fi-mind-bending-movies-that-never-leave-earth/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Faisal Rasool]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/collage-featuring-scenes-from-source-code-district-9-and-in-time.png" length="3098" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Streaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[ Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Streaming]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Take a break from spaceship battles and enjoy some science fiction on terra firma.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p><a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/classic-sci-fi-movies-that-were-inspired-by-star-trek/" target="_blank">Sci-fi movies</a> are typically saturated with aliens, space travel, distant galaxies, and other mind-bending science fiction.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 20:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/grounded-sci-fi-mind-bending-movies-that-never-leave-earth/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Get a Retractable USB-C Charger for $10]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/get-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/the-lisen-retractable-usb-c-charger-with-its-cord-being-pulled-out-for-a-user.jpg" length="299" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Phone charger]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deals]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            It's hard to say no when a deal is over half off.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Right now, you can get a Lisen retractable USB-C charger for just <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGTG9G5F?tag=hotoge-20&ascsubtag=UUhtgUeUpU2016649&asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fget-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10%2F&asc_campaign=Affiliate" target="_blank" class="norewrite noskim" rel="sponsored nofollow">$10 on Amazon</a>. This is a massive 50% discount off the usual $28 price. You can also save an extra $4.20 with the on-page coupon, making this a shockingly low price for a 45W charger that eliminates cable clutter.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 19:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/get-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[This Could Be the Most Underrated Car Brand in North America Right Now]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/could-this-be-the-most-underrated-car-brand-in-north-america-righ/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Brent vd Schyff]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/92_nsx_03-1200x784.jpg" length="112" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Honda]]></category><category><![CDATA[Toyota]]></category><category><![CDATA[Accord]]></category><category><![CDATA[Camry]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Discover why Honda, a consistent performer in the automotive industry, is often overlooked despite its impressive achievements and cult-like following
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Marketing plays a role in the modern game, pushing a narrative and getting in your face more than others. The same spending on the budget might not be possible from every manufacturer out there. <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/best-all-around-family-sedan-2025/" target="_blank">One particular car brand</a> doesn't occupy as much limelight but, however, still continues to deliver rock-solid cars, impressing both those who write about them and those who buy and enjoy them. That brand is Honda.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 19:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/could-this-be-the-most-underrated-car-brand-in-north-america-righ/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[8bitdo's N64-inspired Controller Is 31% Off]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/8bitdos-n64-inspired-controller-is-31-off/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/a-white-and-black-8bitdo-64-bluetooth-controller-next-to-each-other-near-consoles-like-look-like-the-n64.jpg" length="364" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deals]]></category><category><![CDATA[8bitdo]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            This is great for anyone who misses the feel of older controllers.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The 8Bitdo 64 Bluetooth Controller is on sale at its lowest price ever, knocking 31% off the price. It's now just <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DK6VCGBC?tag=hotoge-20&ascsubtag=UUhtgUeUpU2016647&asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2F8bitdos-n64-inspired-controller-is-31-off%2F&asc_campaign=Affiliate" target="_blank" class="norewrite noskim" rel="sponsored nofollow">$28 on Amazon</a>, down from its usual $40. This controller will remind you of the old days on Nintendo 64 and is great for emulation.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 18:24:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/8bitdos-n64-inspired-controller-is-31-off/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Three Note Apps Are Better Than One]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/three-note-apps-are-better-than-one/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Aran Folsom]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/google-keep-obsidian-and-microsoft-notepad-logos-side-by-side-connected-by-plus-signs-on-a-workspace-background-with-a-notebook-pencil-plant-and-coffee-cup.png" length="2390" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apps & Web Apps]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            A journey through note-taking apps leads to an unexpected trio of tools.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>I spent years trying to find the perfect note-taking app and came close with Google Keep. For a while, this app provided everything I was looking for and then some. However, as my needs began to expand, I slowly outgrew it.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 18:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/three-note-apps-are-better-than-one/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Logitech’s New Gaming Mouse Has Customizable Haptic Feedback]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/logitechs-new-gaming-mouse-has-customizable-haptic-feedback/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/a-pink-pro-x-superlight-2c-mouse-on-a-mousepad-next-to-a-keyboard.jpg" length="309" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Windows]]></category><category><![CDATA[mouse]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            The Logitech Pro X Superlight 2c and Pro X2 Superstrike have arrived.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Logitech G just revealed two new gaming mice in its PRO Series. The Pro X Superlight 2c is a smaller version of the popular Pro X Superlight 2, while the Pro X2 Superstrike comes with a brand new, industry-first click technology that supposedly will be a game changer for players.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 18:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/logitechs-new-gaming-mouse-has-customizable-haptic-feedback/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[You Probably Already Have the Perfect Solution to Your Drawer of Tangled Cables]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/you-probably-already-have-the-perfect-solution-to-your-drawer-of-tangled-cables/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Bertel King]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/illustration-of-a-wooden-dresser-with-an-open-drawer-full-of-tangled-cables.png" length="3815" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Hobbies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Phone charger]]></category><category><![CDATA[USB-C]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Next time you reach in, may you only pull out the cord you actuality want. 
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>We all have a junk drawer filled with inaccessible cables. Fortunately, you don't need to run out and buy a fancy organizer. The ideal solution may already be lying around in your kitchen.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 17:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/you-probably-already-have-the-perfect-solution-to-your-drawer-of-tangled-cables/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Nothing's Custom Android OS Is Getting an 'Extra Dark Mode']]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/nothings-custom-android-os-is-getting-an-extra-dark-mode/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/a-green-nothing-os-next-to-a-blue-version.jpg" length="135" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nothing]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Still no release date though.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Nothing just gave everyone a sneak peek at Nothing OS 4.0, the upcoming Android 16 update for its phones. While an exact release date hasn't been given, we can expect the upgrade to come with things like an Extra dark mode, and visual and functional improvements.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 17:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/nothings-custom-android-os-is-getting-an-extra-dark-mode/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[The 10 Most Fun Used Sports Cars Under $30k]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/most-fun-used-sports-cars-under-30k/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tyler Dupont]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/bmw-z4_roadster-2014-hd-e95d55011bf1cf0de7e3a3de6dbdd535c797210da.jpg" length="293" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports Cars]]></category><category><![CDATA[Luxury Cars]]></category><description><![CDATA[
